Indonesian Energy Minister Subroto OPEC deliberately production ceiling 15.8 mln barrel defend 18 dlr barrel price target. He told reporter energy conference Jakarta OPEC decide maintain price level 18 dlrs. "We deliberately defend price OPEC production 15.8 (mln) moment" stated. Asked OPEC increase production price above 18 dlrs barrel decide OPEC meeting June. "We discus market situation then" added. He meeting OPEC Differentials Committee postpone "there meeting." He elaborate. The committee originally due meet Vienna week. REUTER 